1370: Sifridus moved to Die Camp.B.15 after marriage.
Got married to Zuanelt at age 26 in 1370.
Had a son with Zuanelt, Wernerus, at age 26.
1373: Had a daughter with Zuanelt, Lelien, at age 29.
Lost daughter Lelien when Lelien was 1 years old.
1375: Had a daughter with Zuanelt, Clementia, at age 31.
1376: Lost his wife Zuanelt while she was giving birth to Segher in 1376.
Became caretaker of Wernerus, Clementia, Segher at age 33.
1382: Lost son Segher when Segher was 7 years old.
1383: Lost son Wernerus when Wernerus was 14 years old.
Has seen several of their children die.
